result.name: Canton's Kitchen

reviews.text: Good food and service.  Our favorite dishes included the spicy cucumbers,  xui mai with crab roe, and xui mai with quail egg.  Pricing was very reasonable.
Reasonably priced Dim Dum at all Times!
The dim sum are good, no Neff to go to the Chinese restaurant cos better than most of those around the area
Good food, for the price which is cheap. An easy ordering system if you don't speak Cantonese and friendly, if not 100% clean decor...
Still as good as my visit 5 years ago. Reasonably good food even at close to 9pm. Will visit again, hope they don't move again.

result.name: 粵廚點心專門店

reviews.text: 點心即叫即蒸，脆皮鮮蝦腸粉有特色，不是用油條做脆皮的，油麻地店地方比較寬敞，深水埗店地方比較擠逼。
點心大多夠熱和美味，惟服務態度極須改善。
唔算好食，價錢偏貴，但地方企理清潔，比一般點心鋪頭好，雞翼尖千祈咪叫，又貴又唔好食，反而蝦腸就不錯。質素遠不及地鐵之友唐記。
食物還可以.地方一般
